-- China Urges Restraint on Korean Peninsula: Xinhua
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-04-10T23:23:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-10/china-urges-restraint-on-korean-peninsula-xinhua-correct-.html
(Corrects name of media source in first paragraph.)  China urged all parties to
remain calm and show restraint to prevent increased
tensions on the Korean peninsula, Xinhua News Agency
reported, citing foreign ministry spokesman Liu Weimin at a
regular press briefing in Beijing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
